{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Twenty-five-and-a-quarter years ago I read"},{"time":2000,"text":"a newspaper article which said"},{"time":4000,"text":"that one day syringes would be"},{"time":7000,"text":"one of the major causes of the spread of AIDS,"},{"time":9000,"text":"the transmission of AIDS."},{"time":11000,"text":"I thought this was unacceptable. So I decided to do something about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15000,"text":"Sadly, it's come true. Malaria, as we all know,"},{"time":18000,"text":"kills approximately one million people a year."},{"time":21000,"text":"The reuse of syringes now exceeds that"},{"time":23000,"text":"and kills 1.3 million people a year."},{"time":28000,"text":"This young girl and her friend"},{"time":30000,"text":"that I met in an orphanage in Delhi"},{"time":32000,"text":"were HIV positive from a syringe."},{"time":37000,"text":"And what was so sad about this particular story"},{"time":40000,"text":"was that once their parents had found out --"},{"time":43000,"text":"and don't forget, their parents took them to the doctor --"},{"time":47000,"text":"the parents threw them out on the street."},{"time":49000,"text":"And hence they ended up in an orphanage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"And it comes from situations like this where"},{"time":54000,"text":"you have either skilled or unskilled practitioners,"},{"time":57000,"text":"blindly giving an injection to someone."},{"time":60000,"text":"And the injection is so valuable,"},{"time":63000,"text":"that the people basically trust"},{"time":65000,"text":"the doctor, being second to God, which I've heard many times,"},{"time":68000,"text":"to do the right thing. But in fact they're not."},{"time":71000,"text":"And you can understand, obviously, the transmission problem"},{"time":73000,"text":"between people in high-virus areas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"This video we took undercover,"},{"time":79000,"text":"which shows you, over a half an hour period,"},{"time":81000,"text":"a tray of medicines of 42 vials,"},{"time":85000,"text":"which are being delivered with only 2 syringes in a public hospital in India."},{"time":90000,"text":"And over the course of half an hour, not one syringe"},{"time":92000,"text":"was filmed being unwrapped."},{"time":94000,"text":"They started with two and they ended with two."},{"time":97000,"text":"And you'll see, just now, a nurse coming back to the tray,"},{"time":100000,"text":"which is their sort of modular station,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and dropping the syringe she's just used"},{"time":106000,"text":"back in the tray for it to be picked up and used again."},{"time":109000,"text":"So you can imagine the scale of this problem."},{"time":112000,"text":"And in fact in India alone, 62 percent"},{"time":114000,"text":"of all injections given"},{"time":116000,"text":"are unsafe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"These kids in Pakistan don't go to school."},{"time":120000,"text":"They are lucky. They already have a job."},{"time":122000,"text":"And that job is that they go around and pick up syringes"},{"time":124000,"text":"from the back of hospitals,"},{"time":126000,"text":"wash them, and in the course of this,"},{"time":128000,"text":"obviously picking them up they injure themselves."},{"time":131000,"text":"And then they repackage them and sell them out on markets"},{"time":134000,"text":"for literally more money"},{"time":136000,"text":"than a sterile syringe in the first place, which is quite bizarre."},{"time":139000,"text":"In an interesting photo, their father, while we were talking to him,"},{"time":142000,"text":"picked up a syringe and pricked his finger --"},{"time":144000,"text":"I don't know whether you can see the drop of blood on the end --"},{"time":147000,"text":"and immediately whipped out a box of matches,"},{"time":150000,"text":"lit one, and burned the blood off the end of his finger,"},{"time":153000,"text":"giving me full assurance"},{"time":155000,"text":"that that was the way that you stopped the transmission of HIV."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159000,"text":"In China, recycling is a major issue."},{"time":163000,"text":"And they are collected en mass -- you can see the scale of it here --"},{"time":166000,"text":"and sorted out, by hand, back into the right sizes,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and then put back out on the street."},{"time":172000,"text":"So recycling and reuse"},{"time":175000,"text":"are the major issues here."},{"time":177000,"text":"But there was one interesting anecdote that I found in Indonesia."},{"time":180000,"text":"In all schools in Indonesia,"},{"time":182000,"text":"there is usually a toy seller in the playground."},{"time":184000,"text":"The toy seller, in this case,"},{"time":186000,"text":"had syringes, which they usually do,"},{"time":188000,"text":"next door to the diggers, which is obviously"},{"time":190000,"text":"what you would expect."},{"time":192000,"text":"And they use them, in the breaks, for water pistols."},{"time":194000,"text":"They squirt them at each other, which is lovely and innocent."},{"time":196000,"text":"And they are having great fun."},{"time":198000,"text":"But they also drink from them"},{"time":200000,"text":"while they're in their breaks, because it's hot."},{"time":202000,"text":"And they squirt the water into their mouths."},{"time":205000,"text":"And these are used with traces of blood visible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"So we need a better product. And we need better information."},{"time":212000,"text":"And I think, if I can just borrow this camera,"},{"time":217000,"text":"I was going to show you my invention,"},{"time":219000,"text":"which I came up with."},{"time":222000,"text":"So, it's a normal-looking syringe."},{"time":224000,"text":"You load it up in the normal way. This is made"},{"time":226000,"text":"on existing equipment in 14 factories that we license."},{"time":230000,"text":"You give the injection and then put it down."},{"time":233000,"text":"If someone then tries to reuse it,"},{"time":235000,"text":"it locks and breaks afterwards."},{"time":237000,"text":"It's very, very simple. Thank you."},{"time":239000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":242000,"text":"And it costs the same as a normal syringe."},{"time":244000,"text":"And in comparison, a Coca-Cola"},{"time":246000,"text":"is 10 times the price."},{"time":248000,"text":"And that will stop reusing a syringe 20 or 30 times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"And I have an information charity"},{"time":253000,"text":"which has done huge scale amount of work in India."},{"time":257000,"text":"And we're very proud of giving information to people,"},{"time":260000,"text":"so that little kids like this don't do stupid things."},{"time":262000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":264000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}